Package ispd.motor.workload.impl.task

Class TraceTaskBuilder

java.lang.Object
ispd.motor.workload.impl.task.TaskBuilder
ispd.motor.workload.impl.task.TraceTaskBuilder
Direct Known Subclasses:
ExternalTraceTaskBuilder
public class TraceTaskBuilder extends TaskBuilder
Builds tasks from a List of TraceTaskInfos.
The given TraceTaskInfos are converted into tasks, one by one, and distributed between the masters given as argument to makeTaskFor(Processing), in the invoked call order.
